# Doxygen has a redirect that produces a lot of noise.
# maybe this can be fixed, but it's not important for 
# the utility
https://www.doxygen.org/index.html

# There's always trouble with the CI navigating
# to the LGPL license. It works normally.
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-2.1

# DOIs will always redirect, but we don't care since
# that's the best way to provide links to scientific
# papers
https:\/\/doi\.org\/[^\s]+

# We want Zenodo to redirect to the latest verion
https://zenodo.org/badge/latestdoi/22602327
